author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Elephant Stone performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded January 28, 2025.

Songs:
00:30 “The Imajinary, Nameless Everybody In The World”
09:45  Child Of Nature (Om Namah Shivaya)
13:24  Sally Go Round The Sun
16:35  Darker Time, Darker Space
18:24  The Court And Jury
19:43  Land Of Dead (Hollow Medley)

Rishi Dhir - Vocals, Bass, Sitar
Miles Dupire Gagnon - Drums, Back Vocals
Jason Kent - Keys, Guitar, Back Vocals
Robbie MacArthur - Guitar

Host: Jewel Loree
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Audio Mixer: Rishi Dhir
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Scott Holpainen, Jonathan Jacobson & Luke Knecht
